  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas ne patikke tam\nKUNGAM/ ko wiꞥſch darrija/\nun nokawe wiꞥſchu arridjan.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Juhda uhs\nfawu Weddelli Tahmari : Pa-\nleez Atraitne taiva Tehwa Nam-\nmâ/teekams Seelus mans Dehls\npee-aug/ jo tas fazzija/ ka jachu\nwiꞥſtam arridsan ne irr ja-mirst/\nitt ka wiꞥſa Brahteen/ un Tahs-\nmare nogahje/ un dſhtwoja fawu\nTehwa Namina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu ilgß Laiks bij pa-\ngahjis/ nomirre Suä Meita/\nJuhda Seewa/ pehz to eepreezi-\nnajahß Juhda/ un gahje us aug-\nschu pee farweim Awju-Zirpejeem\nuhs Timnu/ wiꞥſch un Ibras\nwiꞥſa Draugs/ tas Odolla-\nmiteris.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas tappe Tahmarei\npaſluuddinahts un fazzihfs: Rau-\ngi/ taws Tehwozig eet uhs Tim-\nnu fawas Awis zirpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad iſwilke ta tahs Atrait-\nnu Drehbes/ nn apſedsahß ar\nMehteli/ un aptinnahß/ un ap-\nfehdahß preekſch Durvim us to\nZelta-Juhti/( prohti kas tekk)\nuhs Timnu/ jo ta bij redſejuſi /\nka Seelus bij pee-audsis/ un ka\nta wiꞥnam ne bij par Seewu\ndohta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Juhda redſeja to / un\nſchkitte to Mauku effam/ tapehz/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nokthde pee tah-\nmallâ / un fazztja : Nah-\nlaid mann pee tew ee-eet/ jo\nne pasinne to fawu Wedd-\nfam/ un ta fazzija: Ko t\ndohji/ ja tu pee man ee-eef\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija: Es\nſchu tew weenu Ahſino G-\nma-Pulka / un ta fazzija :\ndohd man Kihlu / teekams\nfuhti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas: Ka-\ntahds Kihls? ko man tew-\ndohd/ un ta athildeja: Tan-\nspeeschamajs Gredſens/ un\nAuts/ un tawa Needra/ k-\nwâ Rohka irr/ un tas derw\nxai to/ un eegahje pee tah-\nta tappe gruhta no wiꞥna\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta zehlahß un a-\nje / un nolikke to Apſegg-\nwim/ un apwilke fawas A-\nnu Drehbes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Juhda fuhtija t-\nar fawu Draugu/ to Odo-\nteri / ka tas to Kihlu no\nSeewas Rohkas atxeentu-\ntas to ne atradde.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad waizaja tas tah-\ntas Zilwekus/ fazzidams : Ka-\nta Mauka/ kas us to Zelta-\nti irr fehdejuſi? un tee fa-\nsche ne irr Mauka bijuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas atgreeſahß pee-\ndu/ un fazzija : Es to ne-\natraddis/ un tahs Weetas-\ndis arridsan fatta / ſche\nMauka bijuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Juhda:\n"
    }
  ],
